rson&#x27;s meat consumption, and factory farming it causes suffering the animal circle now counts. Each present-human org is charged an additive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 4 climate_tipping_points → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 8 suffering_focused → 9 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWW1T20gS%2Fitd1O2exdpCkt%2Bd46oImF0qkFCEbGorpJyxNLZnkTS6mRHGybK%2F%2FXpGki1jcajK9wFKaGaefvp1usWPg4DOSBqqUx7Qg9HB0REcHx%2FDrSAsBsXBF%2BT7Ch%2BWMdylnuN2YMlFGDwwuoSlO%2FEmnUl%2FMpgMoSEVT2Bo6eN3McKcSJlGiWI8Bn%2BBaCNwICGC%2BwtGQg3mDj1wYUbEhCzJarJIIxLLYsEDErOIhHIieUSXC6KKlQ74Ia4oOlEsSVg8nyScxWp9sr8%2BiZsURfRJyNenByDT2YwKfW7G%2FVTSoFgaQkSJmuAPHkoEn4Y0MpqMib8AslGHSSBwvVILfJ6xkAKaarMsj0BpuiQIZBMERfuymErgwoAJ2kIrkIiiFCbxvVrQzED%2FlDBLY99gvAGfRwmXSHOzAc%2FGAUVEfMWkQZOKxAEJeUwhQgeGNnxb%2B2f88E1T1cfpY0J9hQcfSJhS4DODsHGlbcDeUqlgmq4g1WL0QUnLio3g40KwKIHPNES3UbgW%2FE%2FEzU7%2FOn4%2Fvjm5HZ%2FBdAVzGlOBhrSTVRE3NGBqy0yHuNiEGH1jyGhLIpLB%2BhT7VCitcsQFRsvaYjLbm5mDJEnIqLTh4yqyQz6PuUC%2FN34k3SYkw%2B6TZbCMt4bOT3B68cbsnFJFsrfayWTKQqaQyJRrtQMd9F%2BcJrhfbTgnvuIoE3XNoHBDon0QqyZIDlQHBhdz9Nz4y%2FLs5PKPo398hSkN%2BRLjWp81HqaP%2BByu8Dhio1UNFsoOUl9lvqA69GKJ6s9CnuKpBTr%2BjEkfOSk43lUQk8l2BkZN%2FTh4sgBMcCEm6rCkbL5AbEw9gfGso2hBdLJQKaFxyyMi2f0b%2BB0V0mue4zlorHVmXAuG1NWqWrJru7ngnt3NBdNHJUhJLHlA%2F2lo1JnGGEZr7JfF52l9RsLVNRW3Pvde1Nzx1qo7Xk7B2B8SHbinHzyaUaDBCN4K1DrE9xhLimhnY3JJY3mfiCmybfzdswe01QbjQmXBL3B98Q65YxKa3ItjGkLjHVffjy4p4mKlio8%2B0%