-eater problem it drives human charities firmly net-negative — every human sustained means more net-negative farmed lives. Presupposes counting wild/invertebrate animals, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot; and like the meat-eater problem it is a near-term animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans). || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 4 climate_tipping_points → 7 animals_matter_a_lot → 10 net_negative_animal_lives" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1v2zgS%2FiuD4HbPzjqOJL%2BnlwPSxNkNmrRBmqJY1IVLS7TNjUTqSCqO283%2B9huSki3HCmrAX1rFGj7zzCtn9OMgolOSxfpcRPTg5OD4GE5PT%2BFeEsZBCwgl%2Bb7EhwWHURZ4fhsWQsbRI6MLWPjjYNwe98a%2BBzWlRQq%2BVzfHRxxhzpTKklQzwSGcI9oJeJASKcI5I7EB8wcB%2BDAlckwWZDmeZwnhqngRAOEsIbEaK5HQxZzo4k0bwhjfaDrWLE0Zn41TwbheneytTqKQpog%2BjsXqNFLlVI85nRHNHunYyY5jfFaW9pCEcyBr7kwBgdulnuPzlMUU0C%2Fr1%2BoYtOFGokg1QFJ0JuNUgZAWTNIjNJkkFHkwhb%2FrOXXe%2BLeCacZDi%2FEGQpGkQqEtawE8yyOKiPgTc9SUJjwiseAUEoxW3IRvq2AMH78ZquY4fUppqPHgI4kzCmJqEdZxa1qwt1RpmGRLyIwac1DRsmEn8HEuWZLCZxpjjCjcSvEX4rrTvw%2FfD%2B%2FO7ocXMFnCjHIqMSDNdFkkCY2Y3nDTIb5sAMdAWDLGk4hksT7xkEptTE6ExNRYeUw5WecOkqYxo6oJH5dJMxYzLiQGrvYj7TQgHXSe6xbLRmvg%2FQLnV2%2Bs5IRq4n5NpZiQCYuZRiITYcyOTIZ%2F8Rrgf23CJQm1QJ1oq4NCgdTEgOsGKAHUJIaQM4zc8Mvi4uz6z%2BN%2FfYUJjcUCk9ictRGmT%2FgcL%2FE4YqNXLRbqjrJQu1hg9ChmOpqfJ%2FIFiZe3VN6HIoDTbfuwcJqeF1gz7XPwXAdAVEsCUhO98w8BRu8R%2FUijE3grqVIx%2Fo4O1cRYjBmmrPqQyAlmcu2fbrNPj1pg7dB1%2BA1ur94hacxEm4Cc0xhq74T%2BfnxNERdrkx9%2Fpvw7%2FOMPfjFRD7z2oAHI9Kg4JbgjgKHIS%2FPWVOYNdhdmgierrfNzy7q5WfnZI1vWQBI8OmUhsdU4oUvBI1CJEHoOEUnIDH1euxPhg9JylHnetJu46BKJ6fIGzmSCbwSW1k34jiyBIiRWTuAFATpDhSSiqp5n4gWTmOFAp1PzH6orxTzFYiByiQw41njI8LkBb4eXH%2B6GLm8twoKy2Vwj%2BwZmPyZdgo7h%2BgijHM4x3VaWw8dPNzdnd3%2B6jMAG4pRgjT7QyCJNhKYh1EyqwNn7CyxmyQhWikuwehPuMZGmWRznyXc0WR65J8B6Zo%2FOX64cHTWGHrMGOTFrk3ik3KIS41WRSXzMS9i2RNPtTMbGjBfE1P8yNpvF9NgyVMf%2FYdF%2Fm8WPrjHZesEGgHVnGgEajjAf3g8hjYnTlXdHEplMMvm1XPcn7KMEdZqehLYzjrotAtaTk3TNb